===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Originally, {{Han compound|亼|兄|ls=ic}} written twice. It originally indicates people answering to a call together or saying the same thing unanimously.

Since the Small Seal script version, the whole character is stylized as {{Han compound|亼|吅|从|ls=ic}}.

